## Hover Effects - MANDATORY

```css
.hover-lift {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}
.hover-lift:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.hover-glow {
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.hover-glow:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
}
```

## Accessibility Requirements

- Clickable elements MUST use `<button>` or `<a>`, NOT `<div>`
- Icon-only buttons MUST have `aria-label`
- Interactive cards should be wrapped in `<button>` or use `role="button" tabindex="0"`
- Sufficient color contrast for text readability
- Focus states for keyboard navigation

## Image Sources (NO rate limits)

- Photos: `https://picsum.photos/seed/{NAME}/{WIDTH}/{HEIGHT}`
- Avatars: `https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img={1-70}`
- Illustrated avatars: `https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed={name}`

## Forbidden

- Text placeholders like "[Image: ...]"
- Empty `src=""` attributes
- Inline SVG paths (use Lucide icons instead)
- Hardcoded hex colors in element classes
- `<div>` with `cursor-pointer` for clickable elements
